# Optional: enables the "Cloud backup" feature (back up boards to the user's own
# Google Drive). Leave unset to keep the feature hidden.
#
# Create an OAuth 2.0 Client ID (type: Web application) in Google Cloud Console,
# enable the Google Drive API, and add your site's origin (e.g.
# https://shravangoswami.com) to "Authorised JavaScript origins". The app only
# requests the drive.appdata scope (its own hidden folder), never full Drive.
#
# Copy this file to .env.local and fill in the id.
VITE_GOOGLE_CLIENT_ID=
